---
import Tipsntricks from "./tipsntricks.astro"
---

<section class="video-wrapper">
  <div class="mirco-service-video-wrapper">
    <div class="mirco-service-cta-wrapper">
      <div class="wrapper">
        <h2>Today, ads often fall flat because people are pros at ignoring them.</h2>
        <p class="mirco-service-cta-heading two">
          They've gotten really good at tuning out anything that screams "buy
          me!" We take a different approach, inspired by the best content
          creators out there.
        </p>
        <h2>We craft content that feels real and genuine.</h2>
        <p class="mirco-service-cta-heading two">
          So the message actually sticks. 
          And, more importantly, it helps build a connection with the people watching. 
          We mix storytelling and visuals to create contentthat is true to the brand and adds value for the viewer.
        </p>
        <h2>Our mission is to shake up the way businesses advertise.</h2>
        <p class="mirco-service-cta-heading two">
          We're all about growing organically and having real conversations with your community. 
          We use strategies tailored to each brand, helping them reach and connect with their audience on a deeper level.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mirco-service-cta-button-wrapper">
        <a
          class="mirco-service-cta-button"
          target=”_blank”
          href="https://app.formbricks.com/s/clzu6zoe50000c8nkwg15thwb">Get in touch</a
        >
      </div>
      <Tipsntricks/>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
   @font-face {
    font-family: "goudy_bookletter_1911";
    src: url("/font.woff") format("woff");
  }
  .video-wrapper {
    background-color: #101010;
    color: #fffbef;
    height: auto;
    width: 100vw;
    max-width: 100vw;
    padding-bottom: 5vh;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  h2 { 
    font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
    font-weight: 900;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  font-size: 3.5rem;
  }

  .mirco-service-video-wrapper {
    height: 90%;
    padding: 30px;
    padding-bottom: 1vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: top;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .mirco-service-cta-heading {
    font-family: "goudy_bookletter_1911";
    color: #fffbef;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .two {
    color: #fffbef;
    padding-bottom: 10vh;
  }

  .mirco-service-cta-wrapper {
    font-size: 2rem;
  }

  .mirco-service-cta-button {
    font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
    font-weight: 900;
    border: none;
    background-color: #fffbef;
    color: #101010;
    font-size: 20px;
    width:fit-content;
    border-radius: 100px;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 10px 50px 10px 50px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .mirco-service-cta-button-wrapper {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .mirco-service-cta-button:hover {
    cursor: pointer;

  }

  .wrapper {
    max-width: 65ch;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 580px) {
    .mirco-service-cta-wrapper {
      font-size: 2rem;
      max-width: 55ch;
    }
    .mirco-service-video-wrapper {
      padding: 15px;
    }
    .mirco-service-cta-button {
      width: 200px;
    }
    .mirco-service-cta-button-wrapper {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      padding-bottom: 5vh;
    }
